{"tid":465863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會聖誕卡寄劉霞","createTime":"2017-11-12T04:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T04:19:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61ae61d51f624c33cb384423d82b1d3ac05970c1","tid":465863,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211722&d=uOfuyJdyU270d4KIX3wekBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4a46e291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211722&h=f7bd4b16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211722</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會聖誕卡寄劉霞<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171112/large/12la3p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171112%2Flarge%2F12la3p6.jpg&h=0028e3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民在支聯會街站為聖誕卡簽名。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波今年7月病逝，事隔4個月，其遺孀劉霞至今仍被中共軟禁，行蹤成謎。支聯會昨起一連多日在本港多區設立街站，以「愛心寄劉霞」為題，邀請市民在聖誕卡上簽名，支聯會稍後會將聖誕卡寄送予包括劉霞在內的多名內地異見人士，以示對他們的支持和祝福。支聯會主席何俊仁表示，劉曉波逝世後，劉霞一直未能自由與外界接觸，外界不知道她的居所，亦不知劉霞情況，支聯會十分憂慮她的精神及身體狀況，他期望心意卡最終能透過其親友，轉送到她手上。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙"}]}